cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.CE, cs.CR 

This paper is about optimizing ranking in e-commerce search, which involves information retrieval (IR) and machine learning (ML) techniques. Therefore, cs.IR and cs.LG are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also proposes a feature extension method and uses RNN, which are common techniques in natural language processing (NLP) and computational linguistics (CL), making cs.CL a likely sub-category as well. Additionally, the paper involves optimization and algorithm design, which are relevant to computer engineering (CE) and cryptography and security (CR), making them less likely but still possible sub-categories.
